---
title: Grilled Salmon & Balsamic Tomatoes with Warm Pesto Pasta Salad & Grilled Veggies
description: This grilling masterpiece gets pretty saucy—with balsamic tomatoes and pesto, that is! Garlicky grilled tomatoes and balsamic vinegar are mixed with butter and parsley to make a savory-sweet topping for your grilled salmon. Plus, no great BBQ would be without a can't-miss cookout side: this warm pesto pasta salad tossed with grilled portobellos and sweet bell peppers.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/grilled-salmon-balsamic-tomatoes-f460c1f0.jpg
